{"tid":831472,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【兔迷】主人去邊, 兔仔跟到去邊+原來兔仔會微笑!! 🌟🌟🏆🏆","createTime":"2018-09-22T03:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T09:54:57.000Z","uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"380504481299b97a61be40ea3103dd39704f3ff3","tid":831472,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:31:27.000Z","msg":"主人走到哪裡, 這隻兔子就永遠跟著走到哪裡。還有, 原來兔子懂得微笑, 以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihSd1mss3bA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DihSd1mss3bA&d=b74JW5A%2BIvF1Daqs8iY0P0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=00428db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihSd1mss3bA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.</span>: 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=b74JW5A%2BIvF1Daqs8iY0P0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2f506c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"550c7e94a5bf5375b930ff8de7402f58d30226cf","tid":831472,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原來牠每次追著主人，牠的囗都會微笑</span>"},{"pid":"59139e31b92b080f8f2383252c136fb3211f09e7","tid":831472,"uid":163554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb0cd7b564f0bf6009e9c0f13e8e720f9e8b0f39","tid":831472,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"59139e31b92b080f8f2383252c136fb3211f09e7","tid":831472,"uid":163554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size